text.tspan: Reports are always run in real time
Reports can be saved, re-run using saved parameters
Report security determined by containing folder
Analytic Snapshots: only Tabular or summary
Displays data from perspective of running user
* no subtotals, custom summary formulas, charts,
plot multiple sets of data on a single chart, compare values, Line-on-Column, Line-onLine, Column-on-Column, Bar-on-Bar
dashboards can be composed of up to 20 components
